    <item>
      <title>伊朗战争对中美关系意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/asia/iran-war-china-us-trump-xi.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于习近平与特朗普的峰会几乎肯定会推迟，加上伊朗战争引发的紧张局势加剧，对美国和中国来说至关重要的问题也陷入了不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/asia/iran-war-china-us-trump-xi.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 06:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国轰炸机从英国皇家空军起飞时英国费尔福德，伊拉克战争迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/europe/iran-uk-raf-fairford-starmer-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国皇家空军费尔福德是 2003 年伊拉克战争期间多次反战抗议的场所。现在，它再次被用作美国在中东执行轰炸任务的基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/17/world/europe/iran-uk-raf-fairford-starmer-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 04:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据特朗普命令，石油开始流经加州管道</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/santa-barbara-oil-pipeline-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2015 年管道破裂导致加州中央海岸发生环境灾难以来，石油一直没有流经该管道。这引发了特朗普政府和州官员之间的新斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/santa-barbara-oil-pipeline-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 03:40:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府寻求在谈判期间罢免古巴总统</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/trump-cuba-president-diaz-canel.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国已告诉古巴，为了让谈判取得有意义的进展，米格尔·迪亚斯-卡内尔总统必须下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/trump-cuba-president-diaz-canel.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于 TSA 部分关闭而未支付费用，机场安检队伍不断增加</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/travel/tsa-airport-delays-shutdown.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位工会官员警告说：“迟早会出现突破点。”一些机场的旅客被告知要提前三个小时抵达。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/travel/tsa-airport-delays-shutdown.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对伊朗的立场是什么？他们可以通过一句话来改变。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/trump-iran-war.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统对提出相互矛盾的立场并不陌生，他的助手称这是他的谈判风格的一部分。但在伊朗问题上，他立场的转变与战争的后果发生了冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/us/politics/trump-iran-war.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲拒绝特朗普要求军舰重新开放霍尔木兹海峡的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/europe/europe-iran-war-trump-hormuz-warships.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然一些欧洲国家表示正在讨论帮助重新开放霍尔木兹海峡的方法，但一些国家拒绝了特朗普总统派遣军舰的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/europe/europe-iran-war-trump-hormuz-warships.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官驳回小罗伯特·肯尼迪的疫苗政策，打击特朗普的健康议程</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/health/childhood-vaccines-lawsuit-kennedy.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家地区法院对几家知名医疗组织提起的诉讼作出裁决，称联邦政府在限制新冠疫苗接种和修改儿童免疫接种计划方面的决定并没有基于科学。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/health/childhood-vaccines-lawsuit-kennedy.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高级官员称古巴准备接受外部投资</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/cuba-us-foreign-investment-businesses.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统发表此番言论之际，古巴全国范围内停电，一名古巴高级官员表示，古巴将采取行动向外国投资者开放经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/16/world/americas/cuba-us-foreign-investment-businesses.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:02:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
